                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d566">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Day</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Woodford</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-03-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 28, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your cable 27th received. Full self-government with indemnity would mean Cuban
                    independence. As to other matters see Sunday’s telegram. Very important to have
                    definite agreement for determining peace after armistice, if negotiations
                    pending same fail to reach satisfactory conclusions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Day.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
